<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Consulta enviada</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Trebuchet MS", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(160deg, #1d1d1d 0%, #352012 45%, #914026 100%);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        color: #f9efe0;
      }
      .panel {
        width: min(680px, calc(100vw - 32px));
        border-radius: 28px;
        padding: 36px;
        background: rgba(255, 251, 246, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
      }
      h1 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.2rem);
      }
      a {
        color: #ffd7a8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section class="panel">
      <h1>Gracias, <%= fullName %>.</h1>
      <p>Recibimos tu consulta. Un coach de CrossFit Atlas te responderá con horarios y planes disponibles.</p>
      <p><a href="/">Volver a la landing</a></p>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>

